        In the Docchi mo Docchi series: V.1 - Docchi mo Docchi (Same Difference) From their offices high in a corporate skyscraper, alpha males Ozaki and Tsuburaya make all the girls swoon. Ozaki's known for his irresistible pheromones, while Tsuburaya's a noble, worldly genius. But when these rivals end up in bed together, who will prove to be top dog? It's seme versus seme - and much more than pride's on the line! Ozaki and the ultimate gifted playboy prince Tsuburaya: both are rivals in the same company. These two men will end up in bed together. Which one will lead? A top x top fight outbreak. V.2 - Docchi mo Docchi!! (Same Difference!!)
